"Hyper-parameter Estimation for the Dirichlet Prior"

The file "alpha.tex" in this directory can be converted 
to a PDF file (on most systems) by running LaTeX.   It compiles
without other input using "latex" or "pdflatex".


"A Bayesian View of the Poisson-Dirichlet Process"

This 50 page review article is available on Arxiv:
       http://arxiv.org/abs/1007.0296

A related theory article is:
   Theory of Dependent Hierarchical Normalized Random Measures
   http://arxiv.org/abs/1205.4159
which is about the related Normalised Generalised Gamma process.
Some test code for this is in "test/ngg_*.c"
	
